      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Assessment of whether input parameters used in validation are equivalent to those in the COU; not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "The validation and COU share nominally equivalent input parameters including pump geometry, fluid properties, and operating conditions. Formal equivalency mapping analysis is not required at MRL 2 and has been deferred."
