    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The six factors designated as not-assessed are consistent with MRL 2 scope and do not constitute deficiencies. The CFD hemolysis model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The assessment team accepts the model for its intended use within the scope described in the package narrative.",
